eat-looking girl.\r\nThey\'re wonderful.\r\nThey have a quality.\r\n\r\n535\r\n00:30:18,723 --> 00:30:22,750  X1:174 X2:547 Y1:070 Y2:457\r\nHe probably thinks l\'m a yo-yo.\r\nWell, l would like to take\r\na serious photography course.\r\n\r\n536\r\n00:30:22,821 --> 00:30:24,708  X1:136 X2:585 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nPhotography\'s interesting because...\r\n\r\n537\r\n00:30:24,773 --> 00:30:28,930  X1:129 X2:593 Y1:070 Y2:457\r\nl wonder what she looks like naked.\r\nit\'s a new art form. A set of aesthetic\r\ncriteria have not emerged yet.\r\n\r\n538\r\n00:30:28,997 --> 00:30:32,643  X1:183 X2:538 Y1:070 Y2:457\r\nl\'m not smart enough for him.\r\nHang in there.\r\nYou mean whether\r\nit\'s a good photo or not?\r\n\r\n539\r\n00:30:32,711 --> 00:30:37,469  X1:146 X2:576 Y1:070 Y2:457\r\nl don\'t know what l\'m saying.\r\nShe senses l\'m shallow.\r\nThe medium enters in as a condition\r\nof the art form itself.\r\n\r\n540\r\n00:30:37,577 --> 00:30:42,312  X1:170 X2:551 Y1:070 Y2:457\r\nGod, l hope he doesn\'t turn out\r\nto be a schmuck like the others.\r\nWell, to me-- l mean--\r\nlt\'s all instinctive.\r\n\r\n541\r\n00:30:42,378 --> 00:30:47,114  X1:149 X2:573 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl just try to feel it, to get a sense\r\nof it and not think about it so much.\r\n\r\n542\r\n00:30:47,179 --> 00:30:52,483  X1:153 X2:569 Y1:070 Y2:457\r\nChrist, l sound like FM radio. Relax.\r\nStill, you need aesthetic guidelines\r\nto put it in social perspective.\r\n\r\n543\r\n00:30:54,220 --> 00:30:57,123  X1:167 X2:555 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know. l mean,\r\nl guess you must be sort of late.\r\n\r\n544\r\n00:30:57,197 --> 00:31:01,705  X1:174 X2:548 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou know, l\'ve got to get there\r\nand begin whining soon.\r\n\r\n545\r\n00:31:01,775 --> 00:31:03,685  X1:198 X2:523 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nAre you busy Friday night?\r\n\r\n546\r\n00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:06,827  X1:291 X2:430 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nMe? Oh, no.\r\n\r\n547\r\n00:31:06,896 --> 00:31:09,996  X1:173 X2:548 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nO