e the two categories.\r\n\r\n616\r\n00:35:20,632 --> 00:35:25,205  X1:154 X2:567 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThe horrible would be like terminal\r\ncases and blind people, cripples.\r\n\r\n617\r\n00:35:25,273 --> 00:35:27,641  X1:129 X2:592 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know how they get through life.\r\nlt\'s amazing to me.\r\n\r\n618\r\n00:35:27,706 --> 00:35:30,390  X1:146 X2:575 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nAnd the miserable is everyone else.\r\n\r\n619\r\n00:35:30,459 --> 00:35:32,794  X1:154 X2:567 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nSo when you go through life,\r\nbe thankful that you\'re miserable.\r\n\r\n620\r\n00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:35,446  X1:156 X2:565 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou\'re very lucky to be miserable.\r\n\r\n621\r\n00:35:36,957 --> 00:35:41,595  X1:149 X2:573 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLook at that guy.\r\nThere\'s Mr. Miami Beach in the pink.\r\n\r\n622\r\n00:35:41,662 --> 00:35:44,314  X1:200 X2:522 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nHe\'s just come back\r\nfrom the gin rummy finals.\r\n\r\n623\r\n00:35:44,383 --> 00:35:46,139  X1:266 X2:456 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nHe placed third.\r\n\r\n624\r\n00:35:46,207 --> 00:35:49,110  X1:144 X2:578 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLook at these guys. That\'s hilarious.\r\nThey\'re back from Fire lsland.\r\n\r\n625\r\n00:35:49,184 --> 00:35:51,934  X1:217 X2:504 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThey\'re sort of giving it\r\na chance romantically.\r\n\r\n626\r\n00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:54,783  X1:229 X2:493 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- ltalian, right?\r\n- Him? He\'s the Mafia.\r\n\r\n627\r\n00:35:54,850 --> 00:35:58,047  X1:195 X2:527 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLinen supply business\r\nor cement and contracting.\r\n\r\n628\r\n00:35:58,114 --> 00:36:01,563  X1:187 X2:534 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nOh, gee,\r\nmess up my moustache wax.\r\n\r\n629\r\n00:36:01,635 --> 00:36:04,320  X1:108 X2:613 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThere\'s the winner of the Truman Capote\r\nlook-alike contest.\r\n\r\n630\r\n00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:08,994  X1:200 X2:521 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou are unbelievably sexy.\r\nYes, you are.\r\n\r\n631\r\n00:36:09,062 --> 00:36:12,772  X1:158 X2:563 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou know what you are?\r\nYou\'re polymorphously perverse.\r\n\r\n632\r\n00:36:12,838 --> 00:36:15,261  X1:209 X2:513 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWhat does that mean?\r\nl don\'t know what that is.\r\n\r\n633\r\n00:36:15,335 --> 00:36:18,151  X1:199 X2:522 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou\'re exceptional in bed...\r\n\r\n634\r\n00:36:18,216 --> 00:36:21,086  X1:123 X2:599 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nbecause you get pleasure in every part\r\nof your body when l touch it.\r\n\r\n635\r\n00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:24,838  X1:128 X2:594 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLike the tip of your nose, and if\r\nl stroke your teeth or your knee caps...\r\n\r\n636\r\n00:36:24,906 --> 00:36:26,978  X1:206 X2:515 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nyou certainly get excited.\r\n\r\n637\r\n00:36:27,051 --> 00:36:31,208  X1:243 X2:478 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou know what?\r\nl like you, l really do.\r\n\r\n638\r\n00:36:31,275 --> 00:36:34,091  X1:215 X2:506 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nBut do you love me?\r\nThat\'s the key question.\r\n\r\n639\r\n00:36:34,156 --> 00:36:36,393  X1:190 X2:532 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl know you\'ve only known me\r\na short while.\r\n\r\n640\r\n00:36:36,461 --> 00:36:40,259  X1:228 X2:494 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl think that\'s sort of--\r\nYeah, yeah.\r\n\r\n641\r\n00:36:40,334 --> 00:36:42,189  X1:262 X2:459 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nDo you love me?\r\n\r\n642\r\n00:36:42,254 --> 00:36:47,493  X1:145 X2:577 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLove is too weak a word for what--\r\nl \"lurve\" you.\r\n\r\n643\r\n00:36:47,568 --> 00:36:51,693  X1:207 X2:515 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl \"loave\" you.\r\nl \"luff\" you, with two \"f\"s.\r\n\r\n644\r\n00:36:51,761 --> 00:36:53,834  X1:240 X2:482 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nOf course l do.\r\nDon\'t you think l do?\r\n\r\n645\r\n00:36:53,906 --> 00:36:55,914  X1:285 X2:436 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nl don\'t know.\r\n\r\n646\r\n00:36:57,714 --> 00:37:00,465  X1:112 X2:609 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWhat do you mean? You\'re not going\r\nto give up your own apartment, are you?\r\n\r\n647\r\n00:37:00,531 --> 00:37:02,386  X1:288 X2:434 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- Of course.\r\n- But why?\r\n\r\n648\r\n00:37:02,451 --> 00:37:04,623  X1:157 X2:565 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nl\'m moving in with you, that\'s why.\r\n\r\n649\r\n00:37:04,692 --> 00:37:07,628  X1:164 X2:558 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- But you have a nice apartment.\r\n- l have a tiny apartment.\r\n\r\n650\r\n00:37:07,702 --> 00:37:10,604  X1:139 X2:582 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- l know it\'s small.\r\n- And it\'s got bad plumbing and bugs.\r\n\r\n651\r\n00:37:10,678 --> 00:37:15,382  X1:126 X2:595 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nGranted, it has bad plumbing and bugs.\r\nYou say that like it\'s a negative.\r\n\r\n652\r\n00:37:15,447 --> 00:37:17,553  X1:295 X2:427 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nBugs are--\r\n\r\n653\r\n00:37:17,624 --> 00:37:21,334  X1:125 X2:596 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- Entomology is a rapidly growing field.\r\n- You don\'t want me to live with you.\r\n\r\n654\r\n00:37:21,401 --> 00:37:25,198  X1:186 X2:535 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- l don\'t? Whose idea was it?\r\n- Mine.\r\n\r\n655\r\n00:37:25,274 --> 00:37:27,511  X1:227 X2:494 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nlt was yours, actually.\r\n\r\n656\r\n00:37:27,578 --> 00:37:29,816  X1:179 X2:542 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nBut l approved it immediately.\r\n\r\n657\r\n00:37:29,884 --> 00:37:31,739  X1:233 X2:489 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou think l talked you\r\ninto something.\r\n\r\n658\r\n00:37:31,804 --> 00:37:36,180  X1:138 X2:583 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nNo. We live together,\r\nwe sleep together, we eat together.\r\n\r\n659\r\n00:37:36,253 --> 00:37:38,458  X1:184 X2:538 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nJesus, you don\'t want it to be\r\nlike we\'re married, do you?\r\n\r\n660\r\n00:37:38,526 --> 00:37:42,324  X1:112 X2:609 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- How is it any different?\r\n- Because you keep your own apartment.\r\n\r\n661\r\n00:37:42,399 --> 00:37:44,821  X1:148 X2:573 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlt\'s there. We don\'t have to go to it,\r\ndeal with it...\r\n\r\n662\r\n00:37:44,896 --> 00:37:49,785  X1:132 X2:589 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nbut it\'s like a free-floating life raft\r\nthat we know that we\'re not married.\r\n\r\n663\r\n00:37:49,856 --> 00:37:52,246  X1:224 X2:498 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThat little apartment\r\nis $400 a month, Alvy.\r\n\r\n664\r\n00:37:52,322 --> 00:37:55,322  X1:176 X2:545 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- That place is $400 a month?\r\n- Yes, it is.\r\n\r\n665\r\n00:37:55,394 --> 00:37:58,363  X1:174 X2:547 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlt\'s got bad plumbing and bugs.\r\nJesus.\r\n\r\n666\r\n00:37:58,435 --> 00:38:02,266  X1:168 X2:554 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nMy accountant will write it off\r\nas a tax deduction. l\'ll pay for it.\r\n\r\n667\r\n00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:04,861  X1:164 X2:558 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou don\'t think l\'m smart enough\r\nto be serious about.\r\n\r\n668\r\n00:38:04,933 --> 00:38:06,526  X1:247 X2:475 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nDon\'t be ridiculous.\r\n\r\n669\r\n00:38:06,597 --> 00:38:10,689  X1:117 X2:605 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThen why are you always pushing me\r\nto take college courses like l was dumb?\r\n\r\n670\r\n00:38:10,758 --> 00:38:12,831  X1:138 X2:584 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nAdult education is a wonderful thing!\r\n\r\n671\r\n00:38:12,903 --> 00:38:16,035  X1:185 X2:537 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou meet a lot of interesting\r\nprofessors. lt\'s stimulating.\r\n\r\n672\r\n00:38:28,139 --> 00:38:32,264  X1:151 X2:570 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nDoes this sound like a good course:\r\n\"Modern American Poetry\"?\r\n\r\n673\r\n00:38:33,292 --> 00:38:35,180  X1:278 X2:443 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nOr, let\'s see...\r\n\r\n674\r\n00:38:35,244 --> 00:38:39,174  X1:196 X2:525 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nmaybe l should take\r\n\"lntroduction to the Novel.\"\r\n\r\n675\r\n00:38:39,246 --> 00:38:41,767  X1:143 X2:579 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nJust don\'t take any course\r\nwhere they make you read Beowulf.\r\n\r\n676\r\n00:38:41,839 --> 00:38:43,814  X1:318 X2:403 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWhat?\r\n\r\n677\r\n00:38:43,887 --> 00:38:48,111  X1:162 X2:559 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWhat do you think? Should we go\r\nto that party in South Hampton?\r\n\r\n678\r\n00:38:48,177 --> 00:38:51,494  X1:144 X2:577 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nNo, don\'t be silly.\r\nWhat do we need other people for?\r\n\r\n679\r\n00:38:51,569 --> 00:38:56,240  X1:123 X2:598 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWe should just turn out the lights\r\nand play hide the \"salam\" or something.\r\n\r\n680\r\n00:38:56,307 --> 00:38:59,155  X1:160 X2:562 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWell, l\'m going to get a cigarette,\r\nokay?\r\n\r\n681\r\n00:38:59,219 --> 00:39:04,240  X1:126 X2:596 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nGrass, right? The illusion that it makes\r\na white woman more like Billie Holiday.\r\n\r\n682\r\n00:39:04,309 --> 00:39:07,343  X1:165 X2:556 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- Have you ever made love high?\r\n- Me? No.\r\n\r\n683\r\n00:39:07,414 --> 00:39:10,927  X1:193 X2:529 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlf l have grass or alcohol,\r\nl get unbearably wonderful.\r\n\r\n684\r\n00:39:10,999 --> 00:39:13,869  X1:176 X2:546 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nl get too wonderful for words.\r\n\r\n685\r\n00:39:13,944 --> 00:39:17,719  X1:137 X2:585 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know why you have to get high\r\nevery time we make love.\r\n\r\n686\r\n00:39:17,785 --> 00:39:19,574  X1:278 X2:443 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nlt relaxes me.\r\n\r\n687\r\n00:39:19,641 --> 00:39:22,097  X1:155 X2:567 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou have to be artificially relaxed\r\nbefore we can go to bed?\r\n\r\n688\r\n00:39:22,170 --> 00:39:24,243  X1:162 X2:560 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWhat\'s the difference, anyway?\r\n\r\n689\r\n00:39:24,314 --> 00:39:26,835  X1:145 X2:576 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl\'ll give you a shot of Sodium\r\nPentothal. You can sleep through it.\r\n\r\n690\r\n00:39:26,906 --> 00:39:30,137  X1:127 X2:595 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLook who\'s talking! You\'ve been seeing\r\na psychiatrist for 15 years.\r\n\r\n691\r\n00:39:30,204 --> 00:39:33,620  X1:161 X2:561 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou should smoke some of this.\r\nYou\'d be off the couch in no time.\r\n\r\n692\r\n00:39:33,693 --> 00:39:35,832  X1:174 X2:548 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- Come on, you don\'t need that.\r\n- What are you doing?\r\n\r\n693\r\n00:39:35,901 --> 00:39:39,448  X1:184 X2:537 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- No, Alvy, please?\r\n- You can live without it once.\r\n\r\n694\r\n00:39:41,343 --> 00:39:43,351  X1:218 X2:504 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWait, l got a great idea.\r\n\r\n695\r\n00:39:44,576 --> 00:39:49,050  X1:189 X2:532 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nHang in there for a second.\r\nl got a little erotic artifact...\r\n\r\n696\r\n00:39:49,121 --> 00:39:53,051  X1:150 X2:571 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nthat l brought up from the city,\r\nwhich l think is going to be perfect.\r\n\r\n697\r\n00:39:53,122 --> 00:39:56,800  X1:205 X2:516 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThere. Create a little\r\nold New Orleans essence.\r\n\r\n698\r\n00:39:56,867 --> 00:40:01,93  X1:143 X2:579 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nNow we can go about our business...\r\n\r\n699\r\n00:40:00,004 --> 00:40:02,786  X1:172 X2:550 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nand even develop photographs\r\nif we want to.\r\n\r\n700\r\n00:40:09,670 --> 00:40:12,322  X1:225 X2:497 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- ls something wrong?\r\n- No, why?\r\n\r\n701\r\n00:40:12,391 --> 00:40:15,207  X1:217 X2:504 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know.\r\nlt\'s like you\'re removed.\r\n\r\n702\r\n00:40:15,272 --> 00:40:17,159  X1:290 X2:431 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nNo, l\'m fine.\r\n\r\n703\r\n00:40:17,225 --> 00:40:19,135  X1:314 X2:407 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nReally?\r\n\r\n704\r\n00:40:19,208 --> 00:40:21,730  X1:205 X2:517 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know.\r\nYou seem sort of distant.\r\n\r\n705\r\n00:40:21,802 --> 00:40:23,777  X1:212 X2:510 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nLet\'s just do it, all right?\r\n\r\n706\r\n00:40:23,850 --> 00:40:27,167  X1:163 X2:559 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWas it my imagination or are you\r\njust going through the motions?\r\n\r\n707\r\n00:40:27,276 --> 00:40:29,447  X1:184 X2:538 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nAlvy, do you remember\r\nwhere l put my drawing pad?\r\n\r\n708\r\n00:40:29,548 --> 00:40:32,364  X1:130 X2:591 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nBecause while you two are doing that,\r\nl\'m going to do some drawing.\r\n\r\n709\r\n00:40:32,429 --> 00:40:34,601  X1:197 X2:524 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nThat\'s what l call removed!\r\n\r\n710\r\n00:40:34,669 --> 00:40:37,539  X1:248 X2:473 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou have my body.\r\n\r\n711