nThe music will start.\r\n\r\n727\r\n00:41:19,801 --> 00:41:22,485  X1:159 X2:563 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl walk out.\r\nPlace looks wonderful from here\r\n\r\n728\r\n00:41:22,554 --> 00:41:25,173  X1:142 X2:580 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou folks look wonderful from here\r\n\r\n729\r\n00:41:25,243 --> 00:41:27,731  X1:206 X2:516 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nAnd seeing you there\r\nWith a smile on your face\r\n\r\n730\r\n00:41:27,803 --> 00:41:30,073  X1:222 X2:499 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nMakes me shout\r\nThis must be the place\r\n\r\n731\r\n00:41:30,140 --> 00:41:33,108  X1:125 X2:597 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl stop, and then l open with some jokes.\r\nThat\'s where l need you.\r\n\r\n732\r\n00:41:33,181 --> 00:41:36,760  X1:138 X2:583 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl\'ll say, \"l just got back from Canada.\r\nThey speak a lot of French.\r\n\r\n733\r\n00:41:36,829 --> 00:41:40,660  X1:129 X2:593 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nThe only word to know is \'John Dark.\' lt\r\nmeans the light\'s out in the bathroom.\r\n\r\n734\r\n00:41:40,735 --> 00:41:44,926  X1:195 X2:527 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- l met a big lumberjack.\"\r\n- Jesus, this guy\'s pathetic.\r\n\r\n735\r\n00:41:44,992 --> 00:41:48,506  X1:191 X2:530 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nLook at him mincing around.\r\nBoy, thinks he\'s real cute.\r\n\r\n736\r\n00:41:48,577 --> 00:41:50,781  X1:223 X2:499 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou want to throw up.\r\n\r\n737\r\n00:41:50,850 --> 00:41:53,720  X1:229 X2:493 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlf only l had the nerve\r\nto do my own jokes.\r\n\r\n738\r\n00:41:55,395 --> 00:41:58,527  X1:119 X2:602 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know how much longer l can keep\r\nthis smile frozen on my face.\r\n\r\n739\r\n00:41:58,596 --> 00:42:00,484  X1:204 X2:517 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl\'m in the wrong business.\r\nl know it.\r\n\r\n740\r\n00:42:00,548 --> 00:42:04,291  X1:281 X2:441 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\n\"But, cherie...\r\n\r\n741\r\n00:42:04,358 --> 00:42:06,911  X1:193 X2:528 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nwhat will l do with this, eh?\"\r\n\r\n742\r\n00:42:06,982 --> 00:42:10,813  X1:164 X2:557 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nHe 