you\r\npay for the sessions you miss.\r\n\r\n758\r\n00:43:11,278 --> 00:43:15,208  X1:202 X2:520 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nAlvy, you were just great.\r\nl\'m not kidding.\r\n\r\n759\r\n00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:17,964  X1:157 X2:565 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nCollege audiences are wonderful.\r\n\r\n760\r\n00:43:18,033 --> 00:43:21,033  X1:145 X2:576 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou know what? l think l\'m starting\r\nto get more of the references, too.\r\n\r\n761\r\n00:43:21,105 --> 00:43:25,067  X1:131 X2:590 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nAre you? The 12:00 show\r\nis completely different than the 9:00.\r\n\r\n762\r\n00:43:25,138 --> 00:43:29,230  X1:127 X2:595 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl\'m looking forward to tomorrow. lt\'ll\r\nbe nice. You\'ll meet Mother and Father.\r\n\r\n763\r\n00:43:29,300 --> 00:43:31,340  X1:189 X2:532 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nThey\'ll hate me immediately.\r\n\r\n764\r\n00:43:32,404 --> 00:43:35,700  X1:186 X2:536 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nNo, l don\'t think they\'re going\r\nto hate you at all. Contrary.\r\n\r\n765\r\n00:43:35,765 --> 00:43:40,044  X1:156 X2:565 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlt\'s Easter. We\'ll sit down and eat.\r\nl think they\'ll really like you.\r\n\r\n766\r\n00:43:48,857 --> 00:43:50,516  X1:181 X2:541 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nlt\'s a nice ham this year, Mom.\r\n\r\n767\r\n00:43:52,667 --> 00:43:55,537  X1:129 X2:592 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nGrammy always does such a good job.\r\n\r\n768\r\n00:43:55,610 --> 00:43:57,334  X1:281 X2:441 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nGreat sauce.\r\n\r\n769\r\n00:43:57,403 --> 00:44:01,77  X1:250 X2:472 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlt is.\r\nlt\'s dynamite ham.\r\n\r\n770\r\n00:44:05,117 --> 00:44:07,900  X1:193 X2:528 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWe went to the swap meet.\r\n\r\n771\r\n00:44:07,966 --> 00:44:10,934  X1:175 X2:546 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nAnnie, Gram and l.\r\nGot some nice picture frames.\r\n\r\n772\r\n00:44:11,007 --> 00:44:14,357  X1:202 X2:520 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWe really had a good time.\r\n\r\n773\r\n00:44:14,432 --> 00:44:18,623  X1:174 X2:548 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nAnn tells us you\'ve been seeing\r\na psychiatris