> 00:45:16,523  X1:214 X2:507 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nls that a reason to steal\r\nfrom your partner?\r\n\r\n790\r\n00:45:16,593 --> 00:45:18,960  X1:233 X2:488 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou don\'t know what\r\nyou\'re talking about.\r\n\r\n791\r\n00:45:19,025 --> 00:45:20,619  X1:288 X2:433 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nDefend him!\r\n\r\n792\r\n00:45:20,690 --> 00:45:23,243  X1:257 X2:464 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nPass the brisket.\r\n\r\n793\r\n00:45:23,314 --> 00:45:25,770  X1:247 X2:474 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nMo Moskowitz.\r\nHe had a coronary.\r\n\r\n794\r\n00:45:25,843 --> 00:45:27,698  X1:275 X2:446 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou don\'t say!\r\n\r\n795\r\n00:45:28,660 --> 00:45:30,799  X1:129 X2:593 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nHow do you plan to spend the holidays,\r\nMrs. Singer?\r\n\r\n796\r\n00:45:30,868 --> 00:45:32,843  X1:299 X2:423 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- We fast.\r\n- Fast?\r\n\r\n797\r\n00:45:32,917 --> 00:45:36,049  X1:168 X2:554 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nNo food.\r\nYou know, to atone for our sins.\r\n\r\n798\r\n00:45:36,118 --> 00:45:38,126  X1:247 X2:474 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWhat sins?\r\nl don\'t understand.\r\n\r\n799\r\n00:45:38,198 --> 00:45:39,987  X1:272 X2:449 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nNeither do we.\r\n\r\n800\r\n00:45:41,976 --> 00:45:44,627  X1:207 X2:515 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nHi, Duane. How\'s it going?\r\n\r\n801\r\n00:45:44,696 --> 00:45:48,560  X1:219 X2:503 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- This is my room.\r\n- Oh, yeah? lt\'s terrific.\r\n\r\n802\r\n00:45:48,633 --> 00:45:50,543  X1:202 X2:519 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nCan l confess something?\r\n\r\n803\r\n00:45:55,803 --> 00:45:58,935  X1:147 X2:574 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl tell you this, because, as an artist,\r\nl think you\'ll understand.\r\n\r\n804\r\n00:46:01,789 --> 00:46:04,659  X1:183 X2:538 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nSometimes when l\'m driving...\r\n\r\n805\r\n00:46:04,733 --> 00:46:06,621  X1:232 X2:490 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\non the road at night...\r\n\r\n806\r\n00:46:06,687 --> 00:46:10,004  X1:210 X2:512 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl see two headlights\r\ncoming toward me, fast.\r\n\r\n807\r\n00:46:10,079 --> 00:4