:53:43,897 --> 00:53:45,785  X1:267 X2:454 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWho said that?\r\n\r\n948\r\n00:53:48,411 --> 00:53:51,129  X1:147 X2:574 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nl don\'t know. l think\r\nit may have been Leopold and Loeb.\r\n\r\n949\r\n00:53:55,965 --> 00:53:57,340  X1:328 X2:394 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nHello.\r\n\r\n950\r\n00:54:02,207 --> 00:54:05,306  X1:216 X2:505 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nNo. What\'s the matter?\r\n\r\n951\r\n00:54:06,848 --> 00:54:09,401  X1:246 X2:476 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nYou sound terrible.\r\n\r\n952\r\n00:54:09,472 --> 00:54:11,742  X1:243 X2:478 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nNo, what-- Sure, l--\r\n\r\n953\r\n00:54:11,809 --> 00:54:13,948  X1:203 X2:518 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nWhat kind of emergency?\r\n\r\n954\r\n00:54:14,017 --> 00:54:17,663  X1:218 X2:504 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nNo, stay there.\r\nl\'ll come over right now.\r\n\r\n955\r\n00:54:17,731 --> 00:54:19,935  X1:246 X2:476 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nJust stay there.\r\nl\'ll come right over.\r\n\r\n956\r\n00:54:20,068 --> 00:54:22,370  X1:262 X2:460 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nlt\'s me. Open up.\r\nAre you okay?\r\n\r\n957\r\n00:54:22,436 --> 00:54:24,925  X1:238 X2:483 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nWhat\'s the matter?\r\nAre you all right?\r\n\r\n958\r\n00:54:24,997 --> 00:54:27,266  X1:160 X2:561 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nThere\'s a spider in the bathroom.\r\n\r\n959\r\n00:54:27,333 --> 00:54:30,913  X1:131 X2:590 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\n- What?\r\n- There\'s a big spider in the bathroom.\r\n\r\n960\r\n00:54:32,551 --> 00:54:36,349  X1:151 X2:570 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou got me here at 3:00 a.m.\r\n\'cause a spider\'s in the bathroom?\r\n\r\n961\r\n00:54:36,424 --> 00:54:40,702  X1:119 X2:603 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nYou know how l am about insects. l can\'t\r\nsleep with that thing crawling around.\r\n\r\n962\r\n00:54:40,777 --> 00:54:43,167  X1:213 X2:509 Y1:334 Y2:409\r\nKill it!\r\nWhat\'s wrong with you?\r\n\r\n963\r\n00:54:43,242 --> 00:54:46,177  X1:159 X2:562 Y1:374 Y2:410\r\nDon\'t you have Raid in the house?\r\n\r\n964\r\n00:54:46,251 --> 00:54:50,922  X1:186 X2:536 Y1:334 Y2:409\r